    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, orange juice sounds easy enough. i'm just a bit nervous about the clotting part since i don't have any symptoms of a clot or anything. if i start the 2mg tomorrow, is there anything else i should look out for or do to make sure it's working properly without having to go in for those annoying blood tests?",
